Promotional discount airfare

Some countries like Malaysia and Singapore promote trading for foreign
visitors during some part of the year. During this period, they offer cheap
air tickets to their country on certain flights. If you can check with the
other airlines during this period, you may get excellent discount airfare,
which may even surprise you.

